  "title": "Cloud Consultant / Cloud Specialist",
  "description": "<p><strong>Cloud Consultant/ Cloud Architect</strong></p><p><br /></p><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li><strong>Strong in Cloud Architecture Design and Implementaiton.  </strong></li><li><strong>Manage Cloud AWS, Azure, Google Cloud Design and Solution.</strong></li><li><strong>Strong in AWS/ Azure Cloud  Architecture and inolvement in Hybrid and Public Cloud.</strong></li><li>Identify, design, architect and provide solutions for customers in support of implementation.</li><li>Work with the presales team to provide technical proposals, presentations and solution bill of materials and RFPs.</li><li>SME for customers' system infrastructure design and requirements.</li><li>Attend design review and provide high level and detailed technical design documentations.</li><li>Propose solution and selection of technologies and products and estimate resources required to develop the proposed solution to meet customer's requirements.</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li><strong>Strong in AWS/ Azure Cloud Architecture Design and Implementation.</strong></li><li><strong>Possess strong Cloud Architecture Design and Implementation experience.</strong></li><li><strong>Good in Stakeholders/ Client Management. </strong></li><li>Familiar with multiple products and solutions such as Microsoft, Redhat, VMWare, HCI, AWS, Azure, GCP, DELL EMC or Redhat Ansible etc.</li><li>Possess System Integrator environment from the Government and Commercial background.</li><li>Proven analytical and problem-solving abilities.</li><li>Excellent interpersonal, Vendor management and customer service skills.</li><li>Only Singaporean</li></ul><p><br /></p><p>We respect your privacy and all communication will be treated with confidentiality.</p><p><br /></p><p>If you have meet the job requirements that we are looking for or wish to find out more on this role, please contact us or apply in-confidence to us with you updated MS Word Resume to : kelvin@starcareerconsulting.com</p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p>*We regret only shortlisted candidate would be contacted.</p><p><br /></p><p><strong>Kelvin Lee (Reg. No. R1872625)</strong></p><p><strong>STAR CAREER CONSULTING PTE LTD (EA License: 20C0353)</strong></p>",
